OL,3,CStricter age checks on sales of knives
OL,4,Conline after Southport attack
OL,6,FPeople buying knives online will have
OL,7,Fto submit photo ID at the point of
OL,8,Fsale and again on delivery as part of
OL,9,Fstricter age verification checks to be
OL,10,Fintroduced by the Government in the
OL,11,Fwake of the Southport attack.
OL,13,FUnder the new two-step system, which
OL,14,Fwill be mandated for all retailers
OL,15,Fselling knives online, buyers may need
OL,16,Fto submit an official identity
OL,17,Fdocument such as a passport or driving
OL,18,Flicence, as well as proof of address
OL,19,Fsuch as a utility bill, before showing
OL,20,FID again when the package is delivered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
