OL,3,CStricter age checks on sales of knives
OL,4,Conline after Southport attack
OL,6,FPeople may also need to submit a
OL,7,Fcurrent photo or video of themselves
OL,8,Fto an online retailer alongside their
OL,9,FID, the Home Office said.
OL,11,FCompanies will only be able to deliver
OL,12,Fa bladed article to the same person
OL,13,Fwho purchased it, and it will also be
OL,14,Fillegal to leave a package containing
OL,15,Fa bladed weapon on a doorstep when no
OL,16,Fone is in.
