OL,3,CStricter age checks on sales of knives
OL,4,Conline after Southport attack
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer had
OL,7,Fpromised urgent action to prevent
OL,8,Funder-18s buying knives online, saying
OL,9,Fit was "shockingly easy" for killers
OL,10,Fsuch as Southport murderer Axel
OL,11,FRudakubana to get their hands on
OL,12,Fweapons.
OL,14,FRudakubana, aged 17 at the time, used
OL,15,Fa knife bought from Amazon to kill
OL,16,Fthree girls at a Taylor Swift-themed
OL,17,Fdance class in Southport, Merseyside,
OL,18,Fin July.
