OL,3,CStricter age checks on sales of knives
OL,4,Conline after Southport attack
OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,7,F"It's a total disgrace how easy it
OL,8,Fstill is for children to get dangerous
OL,9,Fweapons online.
OL,11,F"More than two years after Ronan Kanda
OL,12,Fwas killed with a ninja sword bought
OL,13,Fby a teenager online, too many
OL,14,Fretailers still don't have proper
OL,15,Fchecks in place.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
