OL,3,CStricter age checks on sales of knives
OL,4,Conline after Southport attack
OL,6,F"It's too easy to put in false birth
OL,7,Fdates, parcels are too often being
OL,8,Fdropped off at a doorstop with no
OL,9,Fquestions asked. We cannot go on like
OL,10,Fthis. We need much stronger checks `
OL,11,Fbefore you buy, before it's delivered.
OL,13,F"The measures I am setting out today
OL,14,Fwill be crucial in addressing this
OL,15,Fproblem and are part of our Plan for
OL,16,FChange and mission to make streets
OL,17,Fsafer."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@GO]
