OL,3,CStricter age checks on sales of knives
OL,4,Conline after Southport attack
OL,6,FThe sale of knives with a fixed blade
OL,7,Fof more than three inches long to
OL,8,Funder-18s is illegal in England and
OL,9,FWales, with retailers facing fines or
OL,10,Fprosecution if they breach the law.
OL,12,FCurrent laws require sellers to
OL,13,Foperate an age verification system
OL,14,Fthat is likely to prevent a person
OL,15,Funder 18 from buying a knife, but the
OL,16,Flegislation does not stipulate the
OL,17,Felements of such systems.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
