OL,3,CStricter age checks on sales of knives
OL,4,Conline after Southport attack
OL,6,FAt Rudakubana's sentencing on
OL,7,FThursday, prosecutors said he had
OL,8,Fbought two identical knives from
OL,9,FAmazon on July 13 2024, taking steps
OL,10,Fto hide his identity when he did so
OL,11,F"by using a virtual private network
OL,12,F(VPN), which encrypts personal data".
OL,14,FAmazon said it took its responsibility
OL,15,Faround the sale of bladed products
OL,16,F"extremely seriously" and had launched
OL,17,Fan urgent investigation in relation to
OL,18,F"this tragic case".
