OL,3,CStricter age checks on sales of knives
OL,4,Conline after Southport attack
OL,6,FIt confirmed it used "trusted ID
OL,7,Fverification services" to validate the
OL,8,Fage of customers on orders of age-
OL,9,Frestricted items at purchase, and also
OL,10,Ffollowed an age verification delivery
OL,11,Fprocess requiring drivers to verify
OL,12,Fthe recipient's age.
OL,14,FIn this case, its records showed the
OL,15,Fdriver recorded a year of birth
OL,16,Fconsistent with an adult and marked
OL,17,Fthe recipient as visibly over 25-years-
OL,18,Fold, in accordance with its policies
OL,19,Fand industry practice.
