OL,3,CStricter age checks on sales of knives
OL,4,Conline after Southport attack
OL,6,FThe new measures announced by the Home
OL,7,FOffice on Sunday are to be included as
OL,8,Fpart of the Crime and Policing Bill
OL,9,Fwhich is expected to be introduced to
OL,10,FParliament by spring, with more
OL,11,Fproposals still to come in the coming
OL,12,Fweeks.
OL,14,FIn 2024, Ms Cooper commissioned
OL,15,FCommander Stephen Clayman, the
OL,16,Fnational police lead on knife crime,
OL,17,Fto carry out a full review into the
OL,18,Fonline sale and delivery of knives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
